Privacy Policy
Introduction
Welcome to our Mentor Mentee Connects mobile application ("the App"). Your privacy is of utmost importance to us. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how it is used, and the measures we take to ensure your information is secure.

Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information:

Personal Information:

Name: To identify you on the platform.
Email: To communicate with you and for account verification.
Password: Encrypted for security purposes.
PRN: For unique identification.
Branch: To categorize users.
Date of Joining and Leaving: For record purposes.
Contact Information: To facilitate communication.
Attendance and Marksheet Data: To track academic performance.
Personal Information: Including parent emails and contacts, personal email.
Profile Information:

Image: For profile identification.
Address: For contact and record purposes.
Achievements, Projects, and Other Academic Data: To showcase your skills and accomplishments.
Date of Birth and Blood Group: For personal identification and emergency purposes.
Usage Data:

We collect data on how you interact with the App to improve user experience.
How We Use Your Information
Service Delivery: To provide, operate, and maintain the App.
Communication: To communicate with you regarding updates, support, and other essential information.
Security: To protect our services and your data.
Customization: To tailor the App experience to your preferences.
Compliance: To comply with legal obligations and protect our legal rights.
Sharing Your Information
We do not share your personal information with third parties except:

With your consent.
To comply with legal obligations.
To protect and defend our rights and property.
To prevent fraud or illegal activities.
Data Security
We implement robust security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. These measures include encryption, access controls, and regular security audits.

Your Rights
You have the right to:

Access your personal data.
Correct or update your information.
Request deletion of your data.
Object to the processing of your data.
Withdraw consent at any time.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on the App. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at mentormenteeconnect10@gmail.com.

